      "title": "Concept Diagram",
      "description": "<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 800 520\" font-family=\"'JetBrains Mono', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"30\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">RAP Architecture Layers</text>\n\n  <!-- Layer stack - top to bottom reading, like ABAP -->\n\n  <!-- UI / Fiori -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"55\" width=\"700\" height=\"55\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">UI Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"98\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#166534\">SAP Fiori / OData V4 UI / Business User</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"400\" y1=\"110\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"135\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Service Layer -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"140\" width=\"700\" height=\"55\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"163\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">Service Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"183\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1E40AF\">Service Definition → Service Binding → OData V4 API</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"400\" y1=\"195\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"220\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Behavior Layer -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"225\" width=\"700\" height=\"55\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"248\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Behavior Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"268\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Behavior Definition + Behavior Implementation (ABAP)</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"400\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"305\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Data Model Layer -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"310\" width=\"700\" height=\"55\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"333\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">Data Model Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"353\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#991B1B\">CDS View Entities / Projections + RAP BO</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"400\" y1=\"365\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"390\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Database Layer -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"395\" width=\"700\" height=\"55\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"418\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Database Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"438\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#581C87\">SAP HANA / DDIC Tables + AMDP / Table Functions</text>\n\n  <!-- Side labels -->\n  <text x=\"15\" y=\"85\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">🎨</text>\n  <text x=\"15\" y=\"170\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">🔌</text>\n  <text x=\"15\" y=\"255\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">🧠</text>\n  <text x=\"15\" y=\"340\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">📊</text>\n  <text x=\"15\" y=\"425\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">💾</text>\n</svg></div>"
