  "details": "<p class=\"mb-2\">what operations (CRUD, actions, validations) are allowed on</p><p class=\"mb-2\">a CDS view entity and how they behave</p><p class=\"mb-2\">save/update/delete logic automatically; unmanaged requires</p><p class=\"mb-2\">manual implementation in a handler class for full control</p><p class=\"mb-2\">users can save incomplete changes before publishing (activate)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">node; if omitted, the operation is not allowed</p><p class=\"mb-2\">to a pool class with handler methods for custom logic</p><p class=\"mb-2\">mandatory fields); determinations auto-execute on triggers</p><p class=\"mb-2\">(e.g., set status on create)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">a single entity (e.g., acceptBooking), static actions on</p><p class=\"mb-2\">the whole set (e.g., bulkArchive)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">no obsolete statements, mandatory field controls)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">KEY RULES — RAP BDEF Requirements:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">┌───────────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────┐</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Rule                              │ Description                     │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">├───────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────┤</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Root entity must have a           │ persistent table /dmo/...     │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ persistent table assigned         │                                 │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Child entities must use           │ lock dependent by _Parent      │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ lock dependent                    │                                 │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ authorization master (instance)   │ Enables instance-based auth     │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ on root node                      │                                 │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ field ( readonly : update )       │ Protect fields from change      │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ for admin fields (CreatedBy, …)   │ after creation                  │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ field ( mandatory ) for required  │ Enforces not-null on create     │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ business fields                   │                                 │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ mapping for ... { ... }           │ Maps CDS field names to DB cols │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│                                   │                                 │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Strict(2) is MANDATORY for        │ Required for cloud / SAP BTP    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ cloud-ready RAP BOs               │                                 │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">└───────────────────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────┘</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/rap-arch.svg</p>",
